  "id": "RAW_83d9d5",
  "title": "马超……马超……快起来呀！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247691314&idx=1&sn=119ad3c77a39c7e122bba0e98e116a94",
  "date": "2025-07-18 00:45:00",
  "author": "腾讯云开发者",
  "siteName": "腾讯云开发者",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"md6px6fl13t6\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1ghx\"><span leaf=\"\">你是否曾经：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx11v5z\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">午夜梦回时，发现自己变成了屠龙的勇士、登塔的先锋。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx112fq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">白日幻想时，渴望手握达斯维达的光剑，迎来原力的觉醒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1qlb\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">剧院观影时，期待光从背后照下，传来一句——李嘉图，我们的时间不够了，还要继续参加活动么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx120fb\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">近况低沉时，幻听到一句“马超！马超！快起来呀！”的呼唤，残血反杀carry全场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1e7y\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">作为程序员的你，是否也曾有过这样的中二瞬间？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1dxu\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">毕竟在0和1的世界里，程序员才是造物的神。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1tci\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">2025年7月9日，腾讯宣布旗下</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">经典IP“生肖企鹅”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">首次面向用户开放共创！用户可通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">腾讯混元3D AI创作引擎，设计2026马年主题公仔“马鹅”。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">优秀作品将有机会与腾讯联名，量产并上架Tencent Image（腾讯官方周边商店），为这一国民IP注入全新活力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1tci\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"260\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100207633\" data-ratio=\"0.4499332443257677\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57f85c23-32be-4b9e-56af-6c08a7261300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1498\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57f85c23-32be-4b9e-56af-6c08a7261300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"md6pxfx1tci\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这是自 2010年虎年公仔以来，生肖企鹅首次携手用户，借助混元大模型技术，让每个人都能参与到这一经典IP的创作中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">腾讯云开发者诚挚邀请广大开发者参与共创，谁说代码不是马！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">是时候从日常的bug调试中抬起头，从无尽的需求迭代中站起来，让你心中那个天马行空的创意马超，在2025马年的战场上大杀四方！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">不会设计？没关系！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">不会建模？没问题！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">只要你有创意，AI就是你的神队友！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">即日起至2025年7月27日</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，开发者朋友可</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">登录腾讯混元3D AI创作引擎官网</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，完成注册后进入【赛事】页面，访问企鹅大赛活动官网，即可利用AI技术生成高精度3D模型。平台支持文生3D、图生3D、草图生3D功能，选择“生肖鹅公仔”专属风格，轻松实现创意设计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">大赛官网地址：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">https://3d.hunyuan.tencent.com</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"602\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100207636\" data-ratio=\"1.0419254658385093\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/80360f31-a401-4ea8-9bea-b5b387c83500/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1288\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/80360f31-a401-4ea8-9bea-b5b387c83500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">目前大赛已经有非常多有趣的设计，比如有吃货用户设计的“沙琪马”：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100207637\" data-ratio=\"0.9555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f20f1586-4aaa-4b7f-2dff-79346a81f400/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:291px;height:278px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f20f1586-4aaa-4b7f-2dff-79346a81f400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">比如日常生活中非常多见的谐音梗“条形马”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100207638\" data-ratio=\"0.7768518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3e33364e-b164-4869-7689-c2c254688700/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 294px;height: 228px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3e33364e-b164-4869-7689-c2c254688700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">更多来自开发者的独特创意，期待各位码力超人的参与提交！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">更有海量精美礼品及现金实物等奖励等你拿走</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，而你需要做的仅仅只是使用腾讯混元 3D AI创作引擎实现你天马行空的创意。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"335\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100207640\" data-ratio=\"0.5795795795795796\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/141034a1-1f39-4012-0661-0d4ce4961d00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1998\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/141034a1-1f39-4012-0661-0d4ce4961d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span>\n    </o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">码超，码超，快起来呀！</span></span>\n    </o:p></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">你的创意传奇，从现在开始！</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-font-family&quot;:&quot;default&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:normal;\">点击下方阅读原文一键直达大赛官网</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯云发起生肖企鹅 AI 共创大赛，开发者可利用混元 3D AI 创作引擎设计马年公仔，优秀作品有机会联名量产。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯云发起生肖企鹅 AI 共创大赛，开发者可利用混元 3D AI 创作引擎设计马年公仔，优秀作品有机会联名量产。",
  "summary": "文章发布了腾讯云开发者举办的“生肖企鹅”IP 共创大赛，旨在邀请广大开发者利用腾讯混元 3D AI 创作引擎设计 2026 马年主题公仔“马鹅”。此次活动是生肖企鹅 IP 首次面向用户开放共创，借助混元大模型技术，大幅降低了 3D 设计和建模的门槛，支持文生 3D、图生 3D、草图生 3D 等功能。文章强调即使没有设计或建模经验，只要有创意，AI 就能成为“神队友”。大赛提供了丰厚的奖品，并鼓励开发者积极参与，将创意转化为实际作品，优秀作品将有机会与腾讯联名并量产。本质上，这是一篇以开发者为目标群体的营销活动宣传。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "腾讯开放经典 IP 共创，赋能用户参与设计。",
      "explanation": "腾讯首次面向用户开放生肖企鹅 IP 共创，通过 AI 技术降低创作门槛，让普通用户也能参与到品牌内容的生成中，增强 IP 活力和用户粘性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "混元 3D AI 创作引擎降低设计门槛，实现多模态 3D 生成。",
      "explanation": "该平台提供文生 3D、图生 3D、草图生 3D 等功能，即使不具备专业设计和建模技能，也能利用 AI 快速生成高精度 3D 模型，极大简化了创作流程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过创意大赛激励开发者，推广 AI 创作工具应用。",
      "explanation": "大赛以丰厚奖励吸引开发者参与，旨在激发创意，同时推广腾讯混元 3D AI 创作引擎的广泛应用和影响力，拓展其用户基础和应用场景。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "腾讯宣布旗下经典 IP\"生肖企鹅\"首次面向用户开放共创！用户可通过腾讯混元 3D AI 创作引擎，设计 2026 马年主题公仔\"马鹅\"。",
    "是时候从日常的 bug 调试中抬起头，从无尽的需求迭代中站起来，让你心中那个天马行空的创意马超，在 2025 马年的战场上大杀四方！",
    "不会设计？没关系！不会建模？没问题！只要你有创意，AI 就是你的神队友！",
    "平台支持文生 3D、图生 3D、草图生 3D 功能，选择\"生肖鹅公仔\"专属风格，轻松实现创意设计。"
  ],
